{"tid":2076282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特斯拉中國用戶數據和認證服務 將從美遷中","createTime":"2020-06-23T11:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:01:26.000Z","uid":75656,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aabb206e61c0d205c2b90e52f9f5580488b44838","tid":2076282,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"中國新能源汽車產銷格局發生重大變化之際，中國媒體今日引述特斯拉中國內部消息報導稱，美國電動車大廠特斯拉（Tesla）的中國用戶數據和認證服務，確定將從美國遷移到中國，同時，特斯拉正在中國招聘數據中心工程師、存儲工程師、數據庫工程師等一系列資訊技術運維崗位人員。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，對於特斯拉而言，單月銷量破萬的中國市場，越來越顯示出其重要性，在此背景下，特斯拉在中國的策略出現變化，特斯拉中國用戶數據和認證服務將從美國遷移到中國，即把服務器遷往中國，以解決特斯拉App連接不穩定等問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3206534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3206534&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=7861ceba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3206534&h=6b8907ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3206534</a>"},{"pid":"2abf024e42818ff27ffa58e010b97e14247e2673","tid":2076282,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"正式奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4087fed0beea0c7303f25d1b36ba8474e70faf12","tid":2076282,"uid":10905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2abf024e42818ff27ffa58e010b97e14247e2673","tid":2076282,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"正式奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"中國資料搬番中國姐"},{"pid":"8f9ab27e841c2865085ad862c4d05fdcc8d7bd7c","tid":2076282,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"支那版喺支那造<br />\n用戶data喺支那處理<br />\n所有嘢留喺支那入面<br />\n支爆都唔會影響美國總公司"},{"pid":"d2f90d5b72ba8f17d5d526a302eea328961